    "The remote endpoint is reachable over TLS and exposes Streamable HTTP at /mcp.",
    "The OpenAI Responses API client authenticates to the exact intended Entra resource.",
    "The managed identity resolves to the intended tenant and bounded Azure scope.",
    "The exact Azure MCP Server version, container image, and tool inventory are captured and hashed.",
    "Only explicitly admitted read-only, non-secret tools are callable.",
    "Subscription and resource scopes cannot silently widen.",
